{"tid":1344204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】到底有咩工具可以擊退敵人，又唔犯法？","createTime":"2019-07-21T21:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:36:01.000Z","uid":34475,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"87ac025ee50b00dd7cfcfbb780f793d6eccf6a58","tid":1344204,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:00:26.000Z","msg":"經過今晚元朗警黑合作<br />\n大家都知道有咩事報警是無用的<br />\n999會叫你：驚就唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n999會hea你：哦！知道啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（然後cut線<br />\n999會唔聽你電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一般市民，面對凶徒到底有咩簡單工具自衛自保呢？<br />\n我知道之前有巴打組織左強身健體既運動班，但面對手持武器既賤人，我地可以點做，先可以令對方知道自己唔係弱勢易恰，搞我你要付出代價呢？<br />\n<br />\n我諗左好耐，好易入手既cutter、菜刀，有阻嚇性，但太易被入罪（我唔係介意傷害到垃圾sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高級防身既電槍(日本好興用黎防狼個種) 香港難入手，而且可能受管制<br />\n化學d，通渠水漒水易入手，但隨身攜帶有難度同危險性(漏到成袋都係就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n最後諗到較簡單易買既係殺蟲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夏天好多蟲嫁，我最怕蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以隨身帶住枝殺蟲水殺害蟲係好正常合理既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且殺蟲水多數射程較遠，有咩事都可以同對方保持距離<br />\n溫馨提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家用殺蟲水要小心唔好整到自己同朋友既眼仔同皮膚呀，有刺激性嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一缺點係好大長好大枝，唔方便帶(特別係無袋男士同細袋女士)<br />\n<br />\n我暫時未諗到其他了<br />\n唔知各位巴打有無咩好提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b6807ac835e346859f73838d01587c5cde8fd1","tid":1344204,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:02:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d6b54308edf83737c0d90ab6a5c49f1f11da5a7d","tid":1344204,"uid":101092,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:03:21.000Z","msg":"胡椒？"},{"pid":"47abbf15e87b4b6451eb5cd2eb7181c1159cfa32","tid":1344204,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:03:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7c06ff7cb73d9d217b2ad23b777e2c10d40ec033","tid":1344204,"uid":37730,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:04:11.000Z","msg":"你用咩d狗都會入你<br />\n最緊要快上快落"},{"pid":"7193feaf27607f5d6330b075bafed37bd968933d","tid":1344204,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:05:03.000Z","msg":"電筒"},{"pid":"d78dcb2c1e71f6f61c1b30113f2ec9813fd27ef9","tid":1344204,"uid":106533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70ae6f274a7ea7a026ae4c7918cbb02383f2b8e","tid":1344204,"uid":65218,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:09:08.000Z","msg":"呢個時侯仲諗犯唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班係度知法犯法添啦 <br />\n唔夠佢地無賴無恥既決心係無撚用架"},{"pid":"bd000fdd3d632b9650d30cefb87367a49b389dd2","tid":1344204,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:11:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a731e91d7d6daba6bcce1293700eb030007dbdd","tid":1344204,"uid":245484,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:12:44.000Z","msg":"清水都犯法，胸部都可以襲警<br />\n你仲諗唔犯法抗爭呀？"},{"pid":"24fa02d8fdf4043c1d8be9ce4f4b182fae72d883","tid":1344204,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:13:06.000Z","msg":"唔好用鐡通，wo.        會好七痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6505cc8bc81bde133874c8a4bcd4673d61f7df1b","tid":1344204,"uid":34475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a